Monitor.​ViewApp.​ViewModel.​AlgorithmOutputViewModel
ViewModelBase
public
Monitor.​ViewApp.​ViewModel.​AlgorithmOutputViewModel

AlgorithmOutputViewModel class stores the logic & data of the AlgorithmOutputView.  The main goal of the AlgorithmOutputViewModel is to link between the data which related to the health monitoring algorithm output to the UI components.  This class inherits from Galasoft.MvvmLight.ViewModelBase which is the base class for any ViewModel in MVVM pattern.
